    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a masterpiece of automotive history. This isn\u2019t just a car; it\u2019s a preserved moment in time, finished in a deep, lustrous hue that catches the light like a polished jewel. The interior welcomes you with the rich, unmistakable aroma of pristine leather, untouched by the passage of years. Every curve tells a story of elegance, and every mile ahead promises the thrill of a first drive. To own this is to possess a rare relic of perfection, a silent guardian of the open road waiting for its next great chapter.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
