      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! It truly breaks my heart to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for her to find a new home where she\u2019ll be just as cherished. I\u2019ve spent countless weekends keeping her in absolute showroom condition\u2014honestly, she\u2019s so pristine you\u2019d think she just rolled off the line. Whether it\u2019s the way the paint catches the sun or how incredibly smooth she feels on the open road, this car is a total dream for any enthusiast. She\u2019s been garage-kept and pampered every single mile, and I\u2019m really looking for a buyer who appreciates a ride that's been treated with this much love. Come by for a chat and a look; I promise you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
