      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a concours-ready specimen for the true driving purist. This unit features the coveted high-revving powerplant with factory-spec compression verified across all banks. The drivetrain is anchored by a lightning-fast limited-slip differential and a short-throw gearbox that provides surgical engagement. I have proactively addressed the common failure points, installing a reinforced cooling stack and high-flow water pump to ensure zero thermal degradation under load. The suspension geometry has been precision-aligned to optimize lateral G-loading, while the chassis remains incredibly taut. Finished in a depth-corrected factory coat with a multi-stage ceramic seal, the aesthetic matches the mechanical excellence. This is a turn-key, high-performance investment for a pilot who demands a zero-compromise machine.",
      "price": 48900.0,
